{"title":"西藏萨迦格言","authors":["王尧选"],"dates":[{"year":1956,"month":10,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"西藏萨迦格言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"聪明人能勇敢地改正他的错误，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"傻瓜连缺点都不敢承认；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄鹰能啄死有毒的大蛇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乌鸦连小蛇都不敢得罪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在真正有学问的人的周围，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自然有人争先恐后地去请教；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在香气四溢的花丛里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自然有蜂儿像云朵一样聚集。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王尧选译"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔注〕萨迦派是喇嘛教四大教派之一。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}